parameters.name: ImageCacheId
parameters.description: The IDs of the image caches.

parameters.name: ImageCacheName
parameters.description: The names of the image caches.

parameters.name: ImageFullMatch
parameters.description:
Specifies whether the image layers of the image caches must contain all image layers of the container image.\
If you configure MatchImage, you can configure this parameter to further filter query results.

parameters.name: ImageMatchCountRequest
parameters.description:
The quantity of image caches whose image layers contain all image layers of the container image.\
If you configure MatchImage, you can configure this parameter to further filter query results.

parameters.name: Limit
parameters.description: The maximum entries of query results that are allowed to be displayed.

parameters.name: MatchImage
parameters.description: The container images used to match the image caches that you want to query. You can specify a maximum of 100 container images.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. You must specify the token that is obtained from the previous query as the value of NextToken.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the image caches.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group to which the image caches belong.

parameters.name: SnapshotId
parameters.description: The IDs of the snapshots that correspond to the image caches.

parameters.name: Tag
parameters.description: The tags to add to the image caches.
